
<section xml:id="S_0_1_Functions">
  <title>Lines, Slope, and Functions</title>
  <introduction>
    <objectives>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <p>
              What is a function and what do we mean by its domain and range?
            </p>
          </li>

          <li>
            <p>
              What is the slope of a line? What are linear functions and families of linear
              functions?
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
    </objectives>
    <p>
